27
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,000
WHERE WERE YOU?

28
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,400
BIG UPSET WHEN YOU GO
WITHOUT HIM, DOC.

29
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,800
HEY, HE WASN'T AROUND.

30
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,800
