HONEST.

31
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,400
SO WHAT'S IT DOING
OUT THERE TODAY?

32
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,400
SAME AS ALWAYS.
KEEPING ME HAPPY.

33
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,800
HEY, DOC, YOU'RE
A SCIENTIST, RIGHT?

34
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,800
NOT ANYMORE.

35
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,800
THESE TIDAL WAVES, MAN.

36
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,200
THINK YOU COULD, LIKE,
TELL IF ONE WAS COMING?

37
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:49,600
NO ONE CAN, CHICK,
NOT REALLY.

38
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,600
'CAUSE THAT WOULD BE
THE ULTIMATE KICK,

