00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,800
IS TO SURF ONE OF THEM.

40
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,400
HEY, CODY! COME HERE.

41
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,400
COME HERE!

42
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,200
HEY, I LOOKED FOR YOU,
I DID.

43
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,400
COME ON.

44
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,400
YOU HUNGRY?

45
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,600
CONFOUNDING THE PUNDITS

46
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,800
WHO ARGUED AGAINST THE MOVE

47
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,400
INTO TREASURY BONDS
AND NOTES,

48
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,200
DIVIDENDS ARE MUCH HIGHER
THAN EXPECTED,

