00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,200
THE SELECTED COMMODITIES

50
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,200
CURRENTLY UP
FROM A YEAR AGO.

51
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,800
THIS IS AN AREA
