52
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,200
FOREIGN STOCK MARKETS

53
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,800
STILL SHOW LITTLE CHANGE
FROM YESTERDAY,

54
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,800
BUT LOCAL EARNINGS ARE UP.

55
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,600
I KNEW THAT.

56
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,200
THE WORLD'S TOP
DEEP WATER SPECIALISTS

57
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,800
HAVE BEEN CALLED TOGETHER
TO MEET HERE

58
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:32,600
AT THE FAMED AQUATRONICS
RESEARCH INSTITUTE,

59
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,000
FUNDED IN PART

60
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,400
BY WASHINGTON'S NATIONAL
SCIENCE FOUNDATION.

61
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,400
NOW, WITH THE SECOND WAVE
HITTING,

62
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,400
THIS MEETING BECOMES
