63
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,800
OH. DR. AGAMO.
DR. AGAMO, EXCUSE ME.

64
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,800
UH, YES.

65
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,800
