RIGHT.

85
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,800
SURF'S UP.

86
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,200
GO AWAY, FELLAS.

87
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,200
I MEAN IT.

88
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:39,000
YOU'RE COMING WITH US,
DR. WAHL.

89
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,800
AND WE MEAN IT.

90
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,000
YEAH.

91
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,000
JOHN WAHL?

92
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,000
YEAH.

93
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,600
PUT ON YOUR SEAT BELT.

94
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,000
TSUNAMI STAFF,

95
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,800
REPORT TO AREA 6, SECURITY.

96
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:30,000
UH, LET ME JUST SEE
WHO'S HERE REAL QUICK.

97
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:33,200
"DR. HIROSHI AGAMO...
DR. JULES BERNARD."

98
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,400
GOOD.

99
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,000
"DR. JOHN WAHL?"

100
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,200
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?

101
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,600
WHY THEY HAULED HIM IN
ON THIS I'LL NEVER KNOW.

102
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,800
THE MAN'S BEEN
OUT OF IT FOR YEARS.

103
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,400
THEY SHOULD
HAVE LEFT HIM OUT.

104
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,600
THAT'S A LITTLE HARSH,
DON'T YOU THINK?

105
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,600
COME ON. HE WAS THE TOP
IN HIS FIELD, AND HE QUIT.

106
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,400
YEAH, B-BUT THE MAN
MADE SOME, UH,

107
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,600
PRETTY IMPORTANT
CONTRIBUTIONS IN HIS DAY.

108
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,800
I HATE QUITTERS!

109
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,600
DR. WAHL.

110
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,600
JULES BERNARD.

111
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,000
YOU'RE ACTUALLY HERE.

112
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:58,200
YES, SIR. INDEED I AM.
I...I AM HERE.

113
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:01,400
DR. JESSICA WEAVER,
JOHN WAHL.

114
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:04,200
WHY AM I NOT SURPRISED?

115
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,200
NICE TO MEET YOU,
DR. WEAVER.

116
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,200
PLEASE STAND BY
FOR AN IMPORTANT MESSAGE.

117
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:14,200
TSUNAMI STAFF, REPORT
TO AREA 6, SECURITY.

118
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,800
SHE'S CHIEF
OCEANOGRAPHER

119
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,000
AT AQUATRONICS.

120
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,400
SHE HOLDS 2 MASTERS
AND A Ph.D. IN HER FIELD.

121
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,400
THE NAVY PUT HER HERE.

122
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:27,000
AND SHE'S STILL
A LIEUTENANT COMMANDER.

123
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,000
WELL, MAYBE NEXT TIME
I BETTER SALUTE, HUH?

124
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:34,000
SECURITY, AREA 5.
IMMEDIATELY.

125
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,800
I'M EDGAR PURCELL
FROM THE NSA...

126
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,000
I should have known

127
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,200
you'd be here.

128
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,400
I DON'T KNOW ALL OF YOU
PERSONALLY,

129
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,600
BUT, UH,
I KNOW YOUR REPUTATIONS.

130
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,800
WE'RE HERE BECAUSE,

131
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:48,600
AS OF TODAY, 2 WAVES
HAVE KILLED 97 PEOPLE

132
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,200
AND CAUSED WORLDWIDE DAMAGE

133
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,800
ESTIMATED AT OVER
A BILLION DOLLARS.

134
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:55,400
OUR GOVERNMENT...WANTS
TO KNOW WHAT CAUSED THEM.

135
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,200
WAS IT A, UH...

136
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:01,800
SERIES OF TECTONIC
PLATE SHIFTS, DR. AGAMO?

137
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:05,000
MAYBE CAUSED BY OCEAN FLOOR
THERMAL VENTING DISTURBANCES?

138
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,200
OR ARE THERE
SOME KIND OF, UH,

139
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,600
WAVE RESONANCE PROGRESSIONS
WE SHOULD BE LOOKING AT,

140
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,400
SOMETHING WITH
A MATHEMATICAL SEQUENCE TO IT

141
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,200
THAT WE CAN PREDICT?

142
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,400
PREDICT?

143
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,000
NOT THIS, NO.

144
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:19,200
NO IS A WORD
WE DON'T WANT TO HEAR.

145
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:23,600
WHAT WE WANT,
WHAT WE NEED, SOON...

146
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,400
IS SOMETHING DEFINITE.

147
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:28,200
THE JULY 1st
OFFSHORE DISTURBANCE

148
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:31,400
WAS GENERATED IN THE AREA
MARKED IN RED.

149
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,600
95 MINUTES LATER,

150
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:35,400
A 30-FOOT TSUNAMI
HIT HONSHU, JAPAN.

151
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:38,800
THE JULY 10th DISTURBANCE
WAS A RICHTER SCALE 6.5,

152
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,400
GENERATED...HERE.

153
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,600
ONLY 55 MINUTES LATER,

154
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,800
A TSUNAMI HIT
PUERTO VALLARTA,

155
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:48,200
AND THE WAVE WAS SEVERAL
FEET LARGER.

156
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,800
WE CAN CONFIRM THAT

157
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:52,600
THE WAVES WEREN'T CAUSED BY
VOLCANIC ERUPTIONS.

158
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,600
HAVE YOU CONSIDERED
AN ATOMIC BOMB?

159
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,400
SEISMIC READINGS ON BOTH
DON'T INDICATE A BOMB.

160
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,000
IN ANY CASE, ONE ALONE
COULDN'T DO THIS.

161
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:01,200
JIMMY DOOLITTLE
THOUGHT IT COULD.

162
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,200
STANLEY!

163
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,800
YOUNG JOHN.

164
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:06,800
GOD, I MISS SEEING YOU.

165
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,400
HEY, I DIDN'T SEE
YOUR NAME ON THE LIST.

166
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:11,000
WELL, MY LIST.
I PUT IT TOGETHER.

167
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,400
HOW'S THE FISHING?

168
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,200
HOW'S THE SURFING?
GREAT.

169
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,600
YOU MENTIONED A BOMB,
DR. SCHIFF?

170
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,600
NOT JUST A BOMB.
THE BOMB.

171
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:21,000
2 OF 'EM.

172
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,600
THE WAR
WAS WINDING DOWN.

173
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:25,600
WE WERE GONNA WIN.
BUT AT WHAT COST?

174
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,600
JIMMY DOOLITTLE HAD
DONE HIS RAID ON TOKYO.

175
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,200
PRETTY SHAKY
OPERATION, BUT, UH,

176
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,400
PSYCHOLOGICALLY...

177
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:35,000
HE KNEW WE HAD THE BOMB.

178
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:38,600
HIS IDEA WAS TO DROP ONE
IN TOKYO BAY.

179
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,800
GIVE THE JAPANESE PEOPLE

180
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,000
SOMETHING THEY WOULD
UNDERSTAND, SOMETHING

181
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:44,200
THAT WOULD REALLY
GET THEIR ATTENTION.

182
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,800
A TSUNAMI.

183
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,800
DID THE GENERAL HAVE PLANS
FOR A SECOND BOMB?

184
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:50,400
OH, YEAH, HE SURE DID.

185
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:55,800
HE WANTED TO DESTROY JAPAN'S
MOST ENDURING SYMBOL...

186
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,000
MT. FUJI.

187
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:01,600
WE'RE IGNORING METEORS.

188
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:05,000
JOHN LOUIS SAID THAT
MOST OF THEM HIT THE OCEAN.

189
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,200
HE RAN COMPUTER SIMULATIONS

190
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:09,200
ON THE IMPACT TSUNAMIS
CREATED THAT WAY

191
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,600
AND GOT AN AVERAGE
CASUALTY READING OF

192
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,600
100 KILLED, 1,000 INJURED.

193
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,800
ON TOP OF WHICH,
ANY COLLISION LIKE THAT

194
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,600
GIVES YOU A RICHTER SCALE
READING THAT LOOKS EXACTLY--

195
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,800
I-I'M SORRY,
BUT I DON'T BUY IT.

196
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:22,600
NOT THAT I WANT TO DISAGREE
WITH LOUIS. HE'S GOOD.

197
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:26,800
IN FACT, I'M A LITTLE SURPRISED
THAT HE'S NOT IN ON THIS.

198
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:30,800
BUT MY POINT IS THAT
THERE HAVE BEEN 2 WAVES,

199
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,200
ALMOST IN A ROW.

200
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:36,800
THAT IS WAY BEYOND
ANY PROBABILITY SCALE.

201
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:40,000
SO WHAT'S YOUR THEORY,
DR. WAHL?

202
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,600
THE BOMB?

203
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,400
THERE ARE SOME PEOPLE

204
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,000
WITH ENOUGH MONEY
TO BUY AS MANY BOMBS

205
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,400
AS THEY WANT
WITH CHANGE TO SPARE.

206
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:50,200
I GUESS THAT
LEAVES YOU OUT.

207
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,800
THANKS.

208
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:59,000
LOOK, YOU PEOPLE WANT MY HELP,
I'M GLAD TO HELP,

209
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,800
BUT THIS
IS A WASTE OF TIME.

210
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:03,800
YOU WANT METEORS...FINE.

211
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:07,000
FIRST, GET THE GOVERNMENT
TO DO A SATELLITE SCAN

212
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:10,000
OF THE OCEAN FLOOR FOR ANY
NEW IMPACT CRATERS.

213
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,600
ME? I GOTTA GO, UH,

214
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:14,000
DISPLACE A LITTLE WATER
OF MY OWN.

215
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:20,800
AQUATRONICS IS
A NONSMOKING FACILITY.

216
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,400
NO SMOKING, PLEASE.

217
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,400
CHARMING.

218
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,400
YEAH. TALK TO ME.

219
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,400
MR. WAHL,

220
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,400
I'M NOT SURPRISED

221
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:04,200
THEY BROUGHT YOU
IN ON THIS.

222
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,000
IN ON WHAT?
WHO IS THIS?

223
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,400
METEORS! THAT IDIOT.

224
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,200
WHO THE HELL IS THIS?

225
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:11,800
THAT IDEA OF
GENERAL DOOLITTLE'S.

226
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,200
IMAGINE
WHAT A TIDAL WAVE

227
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,200
COULD HAVE DONE

228
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,200
FOR OUR BOYS ON
D-DAY AT NORMANDY.

229
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,800
THINK OF
ALL THE LIVES SAVED.

230
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,800
YOU'RE RIGHT.

231
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:22,000
TOO BAD WE CAN'T
CONTROL MOTHER NATURE.

232
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
HAVEN'T YOU BEEN
WATCHING THE NEWS?

233
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,200
WE CAN.

234
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,400
YOU THINK THAT'S FUNNY?

235
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,800
ARE YOU LAUGHING?

236
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,800
ALL RIGHT, WISE ASS,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

237
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:33,000
