00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:14,400
GIVE ME
A FEW MORE SECONDS.

735
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:37,000
THE COMPUTER ROOM!

736
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,400
SEND SOME BACKUP!

