HE WANTS ME DEAD.

743
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,000
FOR NOW, HE NEEDS ME
TO KEEP THE OTHERS BUSY

744
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,000
WHILE HE GETS READY.

745
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:06,000
READY FOR WHAT?

746
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,600
LISBON.

