00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,400
LOOK, I GOT TO GET
SOMEPLACE,

753
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,400
I GOT TO
GET BACK ONLINE,

754
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:24,400
I GOT TO START CHECKING
SOME THINGS OUT.

755
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,200
WE CAN'T GO
BACK TO MY PLACE.

756
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:27,400
THEY'RE
ALREADY CONVINCED

757
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,600
THAT YOU'RE MAKING
THE TIDAL WAVES,

758
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,400
AND NOW THEY'RE
GOING TO THINK

759
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,800
WE KILLED BERNARD.

