772
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,400
AND BUILD
HIMSELF AN ARK.

773
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:14,000
OH. I'M SERIOUS.

774
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:15,000
AAH.

775
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,000
I GOT THIS PAIN
THAT GOES STRAIGHT FROM

776
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:19,000
THE BACK OF MY NECK
RIGHT TO MY HEAD--

777
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,400
YOU NEED TO TAKE
A SHOWER.

778
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:22,000
OH. YOU TRYING TO
TELL ME SOMETHING?

779
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,000
AS HOT AS YOU CAN
STAND IT,

780
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,400
THEN CALL ME
WHEN YOU'RE DONE.

781
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:26,000
AYE, AYE, SIR.

782
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,400
OH.

783
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:41,400
SHH...

784
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:43,400
MMM.
THAT'S BETTER STILL.

785
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:46,000
SALT WATER IS VERY BAD
FOR YOUR HAIR, YOU KNOW?

786
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:50,400
YEAH, WELL, IT'S
A LITTLE LATE FOR ME.

787
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:53,000
I READ ALL ABOUT YOU
WHEN I WAS IN COLLEGE.

788
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,000
YEAH?

789
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:55,000
YOU WERE
SOMETHING ELSE.

790
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:57,000
YEAH?
I'M NOT THAT OLD.

791
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,400
WAHL?

792
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,400
HMM?

793
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:03,400
I'M JEALOUS.

794
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:05,000
OF WHAT?

795
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,000
OF YOU.

796
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:08,000
YOU DO EXACTLY
WHAT YOU WANT TO DO.

797
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:11,000
AH, IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

798
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:16,400
NOT YOUR USUAL
"WANTED" POSTER, ARE WE?

799
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:22,000
ARE WE GOING TO JUST
KEEP ON RUNNING?

800
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,000
WE HAVE TO.

801
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:26,400
THEY CAUGHT UP
WITH YOU LAST TIME.

802
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:32,400
I LIKE IT WHEN YOU RUB
THIS SIDE RIGHT THERE.

803
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,400
WORK YOUR HAND UP
OVER THIS WAY HERE.

804
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:37,000
OH, I'LL WORK
MY HAND UP.

805
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:41,800
YES, MR. PURCELL.
THAT'S THEM.

806
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:42,600
THANK YOU.

807
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:44,600
I KNEW IT.

808
00:41:44,600 --> 00:41:46,200
I KNEW IT WAS HIM.

809
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:47,600
RIGHT FROM THE START.
I FELT IT.

810
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:49,200
WE JUST FOUND
WEAVER'S CAR

