00:41:49,200 --> 00:41:51,000
SITTING AT THE CURB
AT BURBANK AIRPORT.

812
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,400
WE FOUND THIS UNDER
THE REARVIEW MIRROR.

813
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:56,400
IT'S A MINIATURE
MICROPHONE.

814
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,800
WHAT ARE THEY
PLAYING AT?

815
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,800
SIR? YOU BETTER
TAKE A LOOK.

816
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:07,800
ATTENTION.
INTRUSION, AREA 2.

817
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:12,600
ATTENTION.
INTRUSION, AREA 2.

