00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:20,200
"IF YOU WANT TO THINK
I AM KIDDING, BE MY GUEST,

820
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:23,400
"BUT SOON IT WILL SOUND
LIKE A BARGAIN.

821
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,600
I'LL BE IN TOUCH."

822
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,800
YOU ALL RIGHT?

823
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:48,800
OH, YEAH.

824
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,400
ALL RIGHT.

825
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,400
WHAT ARE WE
LOOKING FOR?

