00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:55,200
NOT "WHAT." "WHO."

827
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:56,600
I ALREADY TRIED GETTING

828
00:42:56,600 --> 00:42:58,200
EVERYBODY'S
NAVY SECURITY PROFILE.

829
00:42:58,200 --> 00:42:59,600
NO, NO, FORGET THAT.

830
00:42:59,600 --> 00:43:02,000
WE'RE LOOKING FOR ANY
UNUSUAL TIDAL WAVE LINKS

831
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,400
TO ANYBODY WHO WAS
AT THE CONFERENCE.

832
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,400
THERE'S NO REASON
STUFF LIKE THAT

833
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:07,000
SHOULD BE CLASSIFIED.

834
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,400
ALL RIGHT,

835
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:13,000
I'M IN THE NATIONAL INSTITUTE
OF SCIENCE CENTRAL FILE.

836
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:14,400
NOW THEN...

837
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:21,400
REST IN PEACE, JULES.

838
00:43:21,400 --> 00:43:23,600
WE KNOW IT'S NOT YOU.

839
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:25,000
YOU NEED A KEYCODE.

840
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:28,600
UM...TRY "TIDAL WAVES."

841
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:32,400
NO. NO, NO,
IT'S TOO GENERAL.

