847
00:43:51,800 --> 00:43:52,800
"SEISMIC WEAPONS."

848
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:58,000
"THERMONUCLEAR..."

849
00:43:58,000 --> 00:44:00,000
YOU SAID
IT WASN'T A BOMB.

850
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:02,000
A TSUNAMI HAPPENS WHEN
THE SEA FLOOR IS ALTERED

851
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:04,000
EITHER BY AN EARTHQUAKE,
A VOLCANIC ERUPTION...

852
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:05,400
BUT WE CAN'T MAKE
THOSE HAPPEN.

853
00:44:05,400 --> 00:44:07,400
AGAMO CONFIRMED THAT
HIMSELF.

854
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:08,800
BUT A TSUNAMI ALSO HAPPENS

855
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:11,200
WHEN THERE'S
AN UNDERWATER LANDSLIDE.

856
00:44:11,200 --> 00:44:12,800
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

857
00:44:12,800 --> 00:44:16,600
WHAT IF
HE'S BLOWING UP MOUNTAINS?

858
00:44:16,600 --> 00:44:17,600
LOOK.

859
00:44:17,600 --> 00:44:19,600
3 LINKED REFERENCES
TO "TSUNAMI"

860
00:44:19,600 --> 00:44:22,000
AND THE WORD
"THERMONUCLEAR."

861
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:24,400
"CRASHER." WHAT'S THAT?

862
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:28,200
IT'S A THESIS PAPER
FROM 1959.

863
00:44:28,200 --> 00:44:31,600
"GENERAL DOOLITTLE'S
FUJI PLAN WAS SOUND

864
00:44:31,600 --> 00:44:33,600
"AND WOULD HAVE ENDED
THE WAR AND SPARED LIVES.

865
00:44:33,600 --> 00:44:35,600
"IMAGINE HOW MANY LIVES
WOULD'VE BEEN SPARED

866
00:44:35,600 --> 00:44:37,600
"HAD A LARGE TIDAL WAVE
BEEN CREATED

867
00:44:37,600 --> 00:44:39,800
AND CLEARED THE BEACHES
OF NORMANDY."

868
00:44:39,800 --> 00:44:41,400
YOU SAID THIS
IN THE CONFERENCE.

