00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,400
NO. NO.

870
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:43,800
STANLEY SCHIFF

871
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:45,800
TALKED ABOUT DOOLITTLE'S
IDEA, REMEMBER?

