00:45:04,400 --> 00:45:06,400
OH...WHAT THE HELL
IS IT DOING?

883
00:45:06,400 --> 00:45:07,600
WHAT?

884
00:45:11,200 --> 00:45:12,000
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

885
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:13,400
WE'VE BEEN AMBUSHED.

