00:45:15,400 --> 00:45:17,000
THAT SCANS EVERYTHING
USING HIS NAME

888
00:45:17,400 --> 00:45:20,000
AND LETS HIM KNOW WHEN
SOMEONE COMES KNOCKING.

889
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,000
HELLO, STANLEY.

890
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:24,400
WHY DOESN'T HE JUST
ERASE THE ARTICLE?

891
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:26,400
STANLEY SCHIFF ERASE?

892
00:45:26,400 --> 00:45:27,400
NO.

893
00:45:28,800 --> 00:45:30,400
"WE HAVE TO TALK.

894
00:45:30,400 --> 00:45:31,600
"MEET ME
AT NOON TOMORROW

895
00:45:31,600 --> 00:45:33,000
"UNDER
LIFEBOAT NUMBER 2

896
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:34,400
"ON THE QUEEN MARY.

897
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:36,400
"IF YOU TELL ANYONE,
