901
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:46,600
"WITH A SWISS BANK DRAFT
FOR THE MONEY.

902
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:50,400
"IF YOU TRY ANYTHING,
THE WAVES WILL NEVER STOP.

903
00:45:50,400 --> 00:45:53,400
J.W."

