00:50:15,800 --> 00:50:16,800
MAYDAY!
MAYDAY! MAYDAY!

956
00:50:16,800 --> 00:50:18,400
GO! GO! GO!

957
00:50:22,800 --> 00:50:24,800
JOHN.
