01:04:58,400 --> 01:05:02,400
"IMAGINE HOW MANY LIVES
WOULD HAVE BEEN SAVED

1223
01:05:02,400 --> 01:05:06,400
"HAD A LARGE TIDAL WAVE
BEEN CREATED

1224
01:05:06,400 --> 01:05:11,200
TO CLEAR THE BEACHES
OF NORMANDY TO..."

1225
01:05:11,200 --> 01:05:15,200
SO DR. SCHIFF WROTE IT.
SO WHAT?

1226
01:05:15,200 --> 01:05:16,800
THAT PROVES NOTHING.

1227
01:05:16,800 --> 01:05:18,800
ALL RIGHT,
ALL RIGHT, UH...

1228
01:05:18,800 --> 01:05:20,800
LOOK, UH...

1229
01:05:20,800 --> 01:05:22,200
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT SCHIFF SAID

1230
01:05:22,200 --> 01:05:23,800
AT THE CONFERENCE
ABOUT DOOLITTLE?

1231
01:05:23,800 --> 01:05:24,800
SURE.

1232
01:05:24,800 --> 01:05:27,800
I THOUGHT HE HAD
MADE IT ALL UP...

1233
01:05:27,800 --> 01:05:28,800
UNTIL I CHECKED.

1234
01:05:28,800 --> 01:05:30,200
OH, GOOD FOR YOU.

1235
01:05:30,200 --> 01:05:33,000
CLARK, RIGHT AFTER
I LEFT AND WENT HOME,

1236
01:05:33,600 --> 01:05:34,600
I GOT A PHONE CALL.

1237
01:05:34,600 --> 01:05:36,000
THE VOICE ON THE
OTHER END OF THE LINE

1238
01:05:36,000 --> 01:05:37,600
SAID EXACTLY
THE SAME THING

1239
01:05:37,600 --> 01:05:38,800
THAT SCHIFF SAID
IN THE ARTICLE.

1240
01:05:38,800 --> 01:05:41,600
OH, WAHL...
STANLEY SCHIFF,

1241
01:05:41,600 --> 01:05:44,200
HE'S GIVEN HIS LIFE
TO WORKING FOR US.

1242
01:05:44,600 --> 01:05:47,200
YES. AND NOW HE WANTS
SOMETHING BACK.

1243
01:05:47,200 --> 01:05:48,200
LOOK, HE KNOWS WE
TRACKED DOWN THAT ARTICLE.

1244
01:05:48,200 --> 01:05:49,600
HE BROKE IN ON US

1245
01:05:50,200 --> 01:05:52,000
AND TOLD US TO MEET HIM
AT THE QUEEN MARY.

1246
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:54,000
YOU'RE JUST
BLOWING MORE SMOKE.

1247
01:05:54,000 --> 01:05:55,400
WOULD YOU LISTEN TO ME?

1248
01:05:55,400 --> 01:05:56,800
I ONLY DESIGNED
2 WARHEADS

1249
01:05:56,800 --> 01:05:57,800
FOR UNDERWATER USE.

1250
01:05:57,800 --> 01:05:58,800
THE FIRST ONE
WAS A BUST.

1251
01:05:58,800 --> 01:06:00,800
THE SECOND ONE
WAS THE MARK-6,

1252
01:06:00,800 --> 01:06:01,800
A COMPUTER-GUIDED

1253
01:06:01,800 --> 01:06:02,800
THERMONUCLEAR
SUBMISSILE.

1254
01:06:02,800 --> 01:06:05,200
SCHIFF WAS THERE
WHEN IT WAS TESTED.

1255
01:06:05,200 --> 01:06:07,600
THE THING HAS A RANGE OF
9,000 MILES, CLARK!

1256
01:06:07,600 --> 01:06:10,600
I THINK SCHIFF
IS USING MY MARK-6

1257
01:06:10,600 --> 01:06:11,600
TO COLLAPSE
UNDERWATER MOUNTAINS.

1258
01:06:12,200 --> 01:06:14,000
THAT'S WHAT'S CREATING
THESE TSUNAMIS.

1259
01:06:14,000 --> 01:06:15,800
THANK YOU...

1260
01:06:15,800 --> 01:06:17,600
FOR TELLING ME
HOW YOU'RE DOING IT.

1261
01:06:17,600 --> 01:06:20,000
IT'S NOT--
IT'S NOT ME!

1262
01:06:20,000 --> 01:06:23,000
IF I COULD JUST GET
INTO AQUATRONICS,

1263
01:06:23,000 --> 01:06:23,800
I COULD USE
THE MAINFRAME.

1264
01:06:24,400 --> 01:06:25,400
I COULD DO
A THERMAL SCAN

1265
01:06:25,400 --> 01:06:26,400
FOR RADIATION
TRACKS.

1266
01:06:26,800 --> 01:06:29,600
OH, MAN, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

1267
01:06:29,600 --> 01:06:31,000
EVERY THERMONUCLEAR
SUBMISSILE

1268
01:06:31,000 --> 01:06:32,400
LEAVES ITS OWN
FOOTPRINT.

1269
01:06:32,400 --> 01:06:35,000
I KNOW THE MARK-6.
IT'S MINE.

1270
01:06:35,000 --> 01:06:37,000
I KNOW
ITS WEAKNESSES.

1271
01:06:37,000 --> 01:06:39,000
SET IT UP, MR. CLARK.
CALL EDGAR.

1272
01:06:39,000 --> 01:06:43,200
HEH. HE WOULDN'T
HELP YOU GUYS...

1273
01:06:43,200 --> 01:06:45,400
EVEN IF YOU WERE DYING.

1274
01:06:47,600 --> 01:06:49,600
THERE'S GONNA BE
ANOTHER WAVE.

1275
01:06:51,400 --> 01:06:53,000
WHEN?

1276
01:06:53,000 --> 01:06:54,600
IT'S NOT UP TO ME.

1277
01:06:55,000 --> 01:06:56,800
DAMN YOU.

1278
01:07:01,200 --> 01:07:02,200
DAMN YOU.

1279
01:07:05,200 --> 01:07:06,600
FORGET IT.
FORGET IT.

1280
01:07:08,600 --> 01:07:10,200
IT ISN'T HIM.

1281
01:07:11,000 --> 01:07:12,000
COME ON, JESSIE,

1282
01:07:12,000 --> 01:07:14,000
LET'S GET OUT
OF HERE.

1283
01:07:16,600 --> 01:07:18,600
GET YOURSELF
A SNORKEL.

1284
01:07:21,000 --> 01:07:22,200
YOU'RE GONNA NEED IT.

1285
01:07:31,400 --> 01:07:33,200
I GOT TO GET
TO AQUATRONICS.

1286
01:07:33,200 --> 01:07:34,800
WAIT. STOP.

1287
01:07:34,800 --> 01:07:36,200
YOU DON'T NEED
THIS ANYMORE.

1288
01:07:36,200 --> 01:07:37,200
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

1289
01:07:37,200 --> 01:07:38,200
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1290
01:07:38,200 --> 01:07:39,200
I'M GONNA TAKE IT
UP TO CLARK.

1291
01:07:39,200 --> 01:07:40,200
I'M GONNA HOOK IT
UP TO THE NET,

1292
01:07:40,200 --> 01:07:41,400
AND LET HIM FIND OUT
WHAT YOU DID

1293
01:07:41,200 --> 01:07:42,200
ON HIS OWN.

1294
01:07:42,200 --> 01:07:43,800
LOOK, HE DOESN'T
TRUST YOU.

1295
01:07:43,800 --> 01:07:44,200
MAYBE HE'LL
LISTEN TO ME.

1296
01:07:44,200 --> 01:07:45,200
I--

1297
01:08:16,600 --> 01:08:19,400
HELLO, CLARKIE.
HOW YOU DOING?

1298
01:08:36,000 --> 01:08:37,400
MR. CLARK,
IF YOU COULD JUST--

1299
01:08:39,800 --> 01:08:41,200
MR. CLARK?

1300
01:08:41,800 --> 01:08:42,800
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

1301
01:08:45,800 --> 01:08:47,000
WHAT...

1302
01:08:47,000 --> 01:08:49,000
MR. CLARK?

1303
01:09:02,200 --> 01:09:03,200
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

1304
01:09:10,400 --> 01:09:12,600
CODE BLUE! CODE BLUE!

1305
01:09:12,600 --> 01:09:15,400
RESIDENT RIGHT NOW.
RIGHT NOW!

1306
01:09:28,800 --> 01:09:32,800
ALL RIGHT, THE MISSILE
HAD TO STRIKE LIGHTNING FAST,

1307
01:09:32,800 --> 01:09:34,400
BUT ITS ENGINE
IS NUCLEAR POWERED,

1308
01:09:34,400 --> 01:09:36,400
WHICH LEAVES BEHIND
A TRAIL OF RADIATION.

1309
01:09:36,800 --> 01:09:40,400
RIGHT. THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE LOOKING FOR.

1310
01:09:40,400 --> 01:09:41,600
ALL RIGHT.
I'M READY.

1311
01:09:41,600 --> 01:09:43,200
ALL RIGHT, START
THERMAL SCANNING IT.

1312
01:09:43,200 --> 01:09:45,200
I'M GONNA GO
BACK TO JULY 1st

1313
01:09:45,200 --> 01:09:46,600
WHEN THE FIRST WAVE HIT.

1314
01:09:46,600 --> 01:09:48,200
LET ME SPEED IT UP
A LITTLE BIT.

1315
01:09:48,200 --> 01:09:49,200
GOOD.

1316
01:09:51,200 --> 01:09:52,600
ALL RIGHT, THERE.
THERE, YOU SEE IT?

1317
01:09:52,600 --> 01:09:54,600
RIGHT THERE. THAT'S
OUR NUCLEAR BLAST.

1318
01:09:54,600 --> 01:09:56,800
UH-HUH. LOOKS
VERY LOW YIELD.

1319
01:09:56,800 --> 01:09:58,400
YEAH. STANLEY SCHIFF'S
SPECIALTY,

1320
01:09:58,400 --> 01:10:00,400
BUT HE COULDN'T GET IT
LOW YIELD ENOUGH

1321
01:10:00,400 --> 01:10:02,600
NOT TO LEAVE SOME
RESIDUAL RADIATION.

1322
01:10:03,000 --> 01:10:04,200
UH-HUH. LOOK.

1323
01:10:04,200 --> 01:10:05,600
THERE'S TIDAL WAVE
NUMBER 1

1324
01:10:06,200 --> 01:10:08,200
HEADING
STRAIGHT FOR JAPAN.

1325
01:10:08,200 --> 01:10:09,000
I'M GONNA
GO BACK AN HOUR,

1326
01:10:09,000 --> 01:10:11,000
SEE IF WE CAN FIND
OUR SUBMISSILE.

1327
01:10:11,000 --> 01:10:15,200
AH, THERE. YOU SEE RIGHT THERE?
THERE SHE IS.

1328
01:10:15,600 --> 01:10:16,800
KEEP BACKING IT UP

1329
01:10:16,800 --> 01:10:18,800
SO WE CAN SEE WHERE
HE LAUNCHED FROM.

1330
01:10:18,800 --> 01:10:20,600
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

1331
01:10:20,800 --> 01:10:22,600
YOU SEE WHERE IT'S
HEADED BACK TO?

1332
01:10:22,600 --> 01:10:25,000
HE LAUNCHED IT
OFF THE COAST HERE.

1333
01:10:25,000 --> 01:10:27,000
WE HAVE TO SEE IF HE'S
BEEN LAUNCHING THEM ALL

1334
01:10:27,000 --> 01:10:28,600
FROM THE SAME PLACE.

1335
01:10:29,400 --> 01:10:32,000
UH-HUH...THERE'S
PUERTO VALLARTA...

1336
01:10:32,000 --> 01:10:33,000
IT'S THE EXACT
SAME SPOT.

1337
01:10:33,000 --> 01:10:34,000
WHERE THE HELL IS THIS?

1338
01:10:34,000 --> 01:10:35,400
LET ME SEE.

1339
01:10:37,000 --> 01:10:39,800
5 MILES STRAIGHT
OFF THE COAST.

1340
01:10:39,800 --> 01:10:40,800
WELL, THERE'S
NOTHING THERE.

1341
01:10:40,800 --> 01:10:41,800
THAT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

1342
01:10:41,800 --> 01:10:44,400
IT'S IN THE MIDDLE
OF NOWHERE.

1343
01:10:44,400 --> 01:10:45,800
WELL, IT COULD BE
A SUBMARINE.

1344
01:10:45,800 --> 01:10:47,400
STANLEY SCHIFF DOESN'T
HAVE A SUBMARINE.

1345
01:10:47,400 --> 01:10:48,800
EVEN IF HE DID,

1346
01:10:48,800 --> 01:10:50,200
IT WOULD STILL LEAVE
SOME SORT OF TRAIL.

1347
01:10:50,800 --> 01:10:53,000
JOHN...WHAT IF HE'S
NOT ALONE IN THIS?

1348
01:10:53,000 --> 01:10:55,400
HE IS. I'D BET
THE FARM ON IT.

1349
01:10:55,400 --> 01:10:57,400
YOU ALREADY HAVE.

1350
01:10:57,400 --> 01:10:58,800
ALL RIGHT, LOOK, LOOK.

1351
01:10:58,800 --> 01:11:00,800
WE--WE KNOW WHERE HE'S
LAUNCHED IT FROM.

1352
01:11:00,800 --> 01:11:01,800
LET'S SEE IF WE CAN
GET A LITTLE CLOSER.

1353
01:11:01,800 --> 01:11:03,200
CAN YOU ENHANCE IT?

1354
01:11:03,200 --> 01:11:04,200
YEAH.

1355
01:11:05,800 --> 01:11:07,200
MORE.

1356
01:11:07,200 --> 01:11:08,800
MORE.

1357
01:11:08,800 --> 01:11:10,200
YOU SEE
WHAT I'M SAYING?

1358
01:11:10,200 --> 01:11:11,200
IF THERE WERE
A SUBMARINE,

1359
01:11:11,200 --> 01:11:12,800
IT'D SHOW UP SOMETHING
BY NOW. MORE.

1360
01:11:12,800 --> 01:11:14,000
OK.

1361
01:11:14,000 --> 01:11:15,600
WHOA. ALMOST THERE.
ONE MORE TIME.

1362
01:11:15,600 --> 01:11:16,600
THERE.

1363
01:11:16,600 --> 01:11:18,400
I'LL BE DAMNED.

1364
01:11:20,400 --> 01:11:21,400
YOU SEE, I KEPT
TELLING THEM,

1365
01:11:21,800 --> 01:11:23,400
BUT THEY JUST WOULDN'T
LISTEN TO ME.

1366
01:11:23,400 --> 01:11:24,800
EVEN WITH ITS ENGINE OFF,

1367
01:11:24,800 --> 01:11:27,400
MY MISSILE STILL LEAVES
A NUCLEAR TRAIL.

1368
01:11:27,400 --> 01:11:30,200
NOT A LOT, BUT SOMETHING.
JUST ENOUGH.

1369
01:11:30,200 --> 01:11:31,800
WHERE DID IT
COME FROM?

1370
01:11:31,800 --> 01:11:35,600
CAN YOU PULL UP A REGIONAL
TOPOGRAPHICAL MAP OF THE AREA?

1371
01:11:35,600 --> 01:11:36,600
UH, I THINK SO.

1372
01:11:36,600 --> 01:11:39,600
SOMETHING WITH CITY
AND COASTAL COORDINATES.

1373
01:11:39,600 --> 01:11:40,600
YEP.

1374
01:11:40,600 --> 01:11:42,000
GOT IT.

1375
01:11:42,000 --> 01:11:43,600
MY GOD.

1376
01:11:43,600 --> 01:11:46,000
WHERE IS THIS?

1377
01:11:46,000 --> 01:11:48,400
IT'S THE BOATYARD
RIGHT NEXT TO THE MARINA

1378
01:11:48,400 --> 01:11:50,400
AT KING HARBOR,
HOME OF STANLEY SCHIFF.

1379
01:11:50,400 --> 01:11:52,400
HE'S LAUNCHING
FROM THERE?

1380
01:11:52,400 --> 01:11:55,600
I DON'T--I--

1381
01:11:55,600 --> 01:11:57,600
I DON'T KNOW.
I GOT TO FIND OUT.

1382
01:11:57,600 --> 01:12:00,000
I GOT TO
GET OVER THERE.

1383
01:12:00,000 --> 01:12:02,400
SOMEHOW I GOT TO GET TO
THE COMPUTER GUIDANCE SYSTEM.

1384
01:12:02,400 --> 01:12:03,800
MAYBE I CAN
DISARM IT ON ROUTE

1385
01:12:03,800 --> 01:12:05,200
OR I CAN ABORT IT
WITH A SELF-DESTRUCT.

1386
01:12:05,200 --> 01:12:06,200
LOOK, I WANT YOU
TO GET EDGAR HERE--

1387
01:12:06,200 --> 01:12:07,600
GET EVERYONE HERE.

1388
01:12:07,600 --> 01:12:08,600
HAVE THEM TAKE
A LOOK AT THIS.

1389
01:12:08,600 --> 01:12:09,600
PUT IT UP
ON THE BIG SCREEN.

1390
01:12:09,600 --> 01:12:10,600
AND WHEN YOU'RE DONE,

1391
01:12:11,200 --> 01:12:12,600
GET BACK TO ME
AS FAST AS YOU CAN.

1392
01:12:12,600 --> 01:12:14,000
WHAT IF HE REFUSES?

1393
01:12:14,000 --> 01:12:15,000
NO CHANCE.

1394
01:12:15,000 --> 01:12:17,000
HE STILL WANTS
IT TO BE ME.

1395
01:12:25,800 --> 01:12:28,400
HE PUT UP
A HELL OF A FIGHT.

1396
01:12:28,400 --> 01:12:29,800
PURCELL.

1397
01:12:29,800 --> 01:12:31,400
WHO?

1398
01:12:31,800 --> 01:12:33,400
PATCH HER THROUGH.

1399
01:12:33,400 --> 01:12:36,000
JESSICA WEAVER
WANTS TO TALK TO ME.

1400
01:14:31,400 --> 01:14:33,400
THAT ONE CAUSED THE WAVE
THAT HIT JAPAN.

1401
01:14:33,400 --> 01:14:35,400
THAT ONE'S PUERTO VALLARTA,

1402
01:14:35,400 --> 01:14:37,400
AND THEY WERE ALL LAUNCHED
FROM THE SAME PLACE--

1403
01:14:37,400 --> 01:14:38,600
RIGHT THERE.

1404
01:14:39,000 --> 01:14:41,800
A BOATYARD
IN REDONDO BEACH.

1405
01:14:41,800 --> 01:14:46,200
LOOK! ANOTHER NUCLEAR MISSILE
HAS BEEN LAUNCHED.

1406
01:14:46,200 --> 01:14:47,400
LISBON.

1407
01:14:47,400 --> 01:14:49,000
WAHL IS CALLING
THIS ONE?

1408
01:14:49,000 --> 01:14:50,600
AREN'T YOU LISTENING
TO WHAT WE'RE SAYING,

1409
01:14:50,600 --> 01:14:51,800
OR IS YOUR OWN
PERSONAL AGENDA

1410
01:14:51,800 --> 01:14:53,000
MORE IMPORTANT
THAN THE TRUTH?

1411
01:14:53,400 --> 01:14:55,000
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

1412
01:14:55,000 --> 01:14:56,200
THERE'S ONLY ONE TRUTH
I WANT HERE--

1413
01:14:56,200 --> 01:14:57,800
THE MAN
WHO'S DOING THIS

1414
01:14:57,800 --> 01:14:59,400
AND YOUR
INVOLVEMENT IN IT.

1415
01:14:59,400 --> 01:15:03,000
THAT'S WHAT YOU SHOULD
BE WORRYING ABOUT.

1416
01:15:05,200 --> 01:15:06,200
OH, HEY,

1417
01:15:06,200 --> 01:15:07,200
UH, STANLEY SCHIFF--

1418
01:15:07,200 --> 01:15:08,200
HAVE YOU SEEN HIM
AROUND?

1419
01:15:08,200 --> 01:15:09,200
HE'S NOT
ON HIS BOAT.

1420
01:15:09,200 --> 01:15:11,200
YOU MIGHT CHECK
HIS SAIL LOFT.

1421
01:15:11,200 --> 01:15:12,800
THAT'S THE LITTLE RED BUILDING
AROUND THE CORNER.

1422
01:15:12,800 --> 01:15:14,200
ALL RIGHT,
THANK YOU.

1423
01:15:30,000 --> 01:15:30,800
STAND BY.

1424
01:15:31,200 --> 01:15:33,200
WE'VE GOT AN EMERGENCY
SITUATION DEVELOPING.

1425
01:15:33,200 --> 01:15:36,200
WHEN I KNOW WHERE IT IS,
I'LL TELL YOU.

1426
01:15:36,200 --> 01:15:39,200
WAHL IS SETTING US UP.
I KNOW IT.

1427
01:17:51,800 --> 01:17:53,200
IT'S LAUNCHED.

1428
01:18:38,400 --> 01:18:41,600
LATE FOR CLASS AGAIN,
MR. WAHL.

1429
01:18:41,600 --> 01:18:42,800
STANLEY...

1430
01:18:42,800 --> 01:18:44,000
THE MISSILE...

1431
01:18:44,000 --> 01:18:45,200
ON ITS WAY.

1432
01:18:46,000 --> 01:18:48,200
DON'T DO THIS,
STANLEY.

1433
01:18:48,200 --> 01:18:49,000
DON'T DO THIS!

1434
01:18:49,000 --> 01:18:50,600
DO WHAT, KILL YOU...

1435
01:18:50,600 --> 01:18:52,400
OR WIPE OUT SAN DIEGO?

1436
01:18:52,400 --> 01:18:54,400
SAN DIEGO?

1437
01:18:54,400 --> 01:18:56,400
NOT JUST 1 WAVE, BUT 2,

1438
01:18:56,400 --> 01:18:58,000
AND TOMORROW MAKES 3.

1439
01:19:01,800 --> 01:19:05,400
NOT EXACTLY YOUR YOUNG JOHN
GUIDANCE DELIVERY SYSTEM,

1440
01:19:05,800 --> 01:19:07,000
BUT IT WORKS.

1441
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:09,000
A DRONE CARRIER.

1442
01:19:09,000 --> 01:19:10,800
OUT THERE
IN THE MIDDLE OF NOWHERE

1443
01:19:10,800 --> 01:19:12,200
SHE DROPS HER LOAD,
TURNS AROUND

1444
01:19:12,200 --> 01:19:15,200
AND COMES CHUGGING
SAFELY BACK HOME AGAIN.

1445
01:19:15,200 --> 01:19:16,600
JUST LIKE ONE OF
THOSE BATHTUB TOYS

1446
01:19:16,600 --> 01:19:17,600
WHEN YOU WERE A KID.

1447
01:19:17,600 --> 01:19:19,400
FOR GOD'S SAKES!

1448
01:19:19,400 --> 01:19:21,400
JOHNNY...

1449
01:19:21,400 --> 01:19:22,200
THEY GAVE YOU
THE PRIZE,

1450
01:19:22,200 --> 01:19:24,000
BUT THEY'RE GOING TO
REMEMBER ME.

1451
01:19:24,000 --> 01:19:28,000
ACTUALLY, THEY'RE GOING
TO REMEMBER BOTH OF US.

1452
01:19:28,400 --> 01:19:30,200
HOW DO YOU THINK
I GOT THE MISSILES?

1453
01:19:30,600 --> 01:19:31,600
I PULLED A TRADE.

1454
01:19:32,000 --> 01:19:33,800
MY SYSTEM...

1455
01:19:36,800 --> 01:19:38,200
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1456
01:19:38,200 --> 01:19:39,200
UGH!

1457
01:19:43,400 --> 01:19:44,800
STANLEY, GIVE ME
THE CODE.

1458
01:19:44,800 --> 01:19:45,800
ARRRR...

1459
01:19:50,800 --> 01:19:52,600
GIVE ME
